Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.47,0:01:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,身为半妖的犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.83,0:01:22.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一心一意想要得到四魂之玉的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.27,0:01:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在得到了父亲的獠牙的铁碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.44,0:01:27.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,反败为胜击败了哥哥杀生丸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.94,0:01:30.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他想要变成完全妖怪的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.51,0:01:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎越来越强了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.11,0:01:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,枫婆婆说
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.38,0:01:39.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要注意千万\N别让犬夜叉随便拿走四魂之玉的碎片
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.89,0:01:40.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.95,0:01:42.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为虽然犬夜叉有铁碎牙
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.89,0:01:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是我也有必胜绝招
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:47.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 给我坐下！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.77,0:01:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊～好舒服哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.97,0:01:58.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,水这么清澈 空气也很新鲜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.94,0:02:00.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从这种地方看来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.31,0:02:02.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个时代也不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.61,0:02:07.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们离开村子都已经三天了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.76,0:02:11.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,四魂之玉碎片会不会已经不在武藏国的境内了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.09,0:02:15.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 你有没有听我说话啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.10,0:02:18.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 有可能呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过年轻女孩光滑的肌肤真是好东西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.90,0:02:23.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说你啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.25,0:02:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我稍微去偷看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.96,0:02:30.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别去了 小心被打个半死
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.43,0:02:37.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉少爷也真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.18,0:02:39.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明自己也很有兴趣嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.42,0:02:49.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,干嘛啊 我又不是来偷看你的！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.12,0:02:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快帮我把衣服拿回来！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.82,0:02:57.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,口哨？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.17,0:03:11.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,乖 日吉丸 辛苦你了
Comment: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,丰臣秀吉：（1536－1598）安土桃山时代的武将 尾张中村人 是织田信长的随从木下弥右卫门之子 幼名日吉丸 仕从信长后因战功显赫而被重用 本能寺之变后 讨伐明智光秀 征伐四国 九州 关东 奥羽 于1590年统一天下 1585年被封关白 次年被赐姓丰臣 成为太政大臣 在文禄 庆长之役中向朝鲜出兵 在没有得到战国的时候病死在伏见城
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.05,0:03:16.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这不是食物！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.93,0:03:20.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点把衣服还给我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们到底是谁？可疑的家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:25.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是我的台词
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.46,0:03:31.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妖怪城主 九十九蟾蜍
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.80,0:03:38.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们很饿了吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.29,0:03:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要喝茶吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.67,0:03:44.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉要不要也吃一点
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.27,0:03:45.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我才不要
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:48.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,帮忙吃掉点东西 我的行李才会轻一点嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.04,0:03:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就说嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.22,0:03:53.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛每次回去的时候都带这么多东西来啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.60,0:03:56.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为要带换洗的衣服 还有作业啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.73,0:03:58.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我说…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.70,0:04:02.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这干芋头真美味
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你了 小姑娘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.05,0:04:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.92,0:04:07.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他叫犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.10,0:04:08.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还有…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.11,0:04:14.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是跳蚤冥加爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.10,0:04:17.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人到底什么来头啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.63,0:04:20.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你刚才说跟随从走散不知如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.41,0:04:23.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是有钱人家的少爷吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.69,0:04:25.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为身负重任 我不能暴露身份
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:31.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫信长
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:35.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信…信长？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.82,0:04:37.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不会吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.89,0:04:39.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请跟我握手～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.37,0:04:41.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后…请你帮我签名
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.00,0:04:42.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,签…签名？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.25,0:04:44.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,写名字 写名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.02,0:04:46.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,记得要写出全名哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:50.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你干嘛那么兴奋啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.47,0:04:52.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是织田信长哦 你不知道吗？
Comment: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,Default,PopSub,0,0,0,,// PopSub注释: 下一行已被修改
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.06,0:00:00.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,织田信长：（1534－1582）战国时代的武将 1560年5月在尾张的桶狭间（今爱知县明市荣町）奇袭今川义元 奠定了信长称霸全国的基础 1573年把将军足利义昭流放 灭亡了室町幕府 建造了安土城开始了统一全国的大业 但中途遭明智光秀奇袭 在本能寺自尽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:54.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他可是超级有名的人物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.97,0:04:57.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他好像不是织田信长哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.91,0:05:02.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,甘利…信长？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.31,0:05:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人！ 原来你不是织田信长啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.11,0:05:06.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是武田的人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.86,0:05:10.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要把我跟那个尾张的愚蠢之辈相提并论
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,愚蠢之辈？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:12.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是指大笨蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.09,0:05:15.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么不早说你不是织田信长啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.41,0:05:18.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉…害我白高兴一场
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.30,0:05:21.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你的款待
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:24.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我身上背负着重大的使命 先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.91,0:05:25.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.42,0:05:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那边是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.09,0:05:34.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边是断崖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明这么愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.90,0:05:38.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,却不是织田信长啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.16,0:05:47.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们把全城的女孩都抓起来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.55,0:05:49.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底要干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说那些被带进城里的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.46,0:05:53.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没一个回得来的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.06,0:05:59.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,竟…竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.76,0:06:02.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原来那些谣传都是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:06.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么我们要跟着这小子啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.62,0:06:09.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我总觉得我们不能丢下他不管嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！我们可是要找四魂之玉…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.77,0:06:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们千万不要说出去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.11,0:06:18.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说城主大人被妖怪附身了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.77,0:06:19.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.76,0:06:33.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露姬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.14,0:06:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,习惯这里的生活了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.49,0:06:39.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…没有任何不习惯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.57,0:06:42.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.88,0:06:45.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请问…主公
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.43,0:06:46.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.27,0:06:48.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听说这阵子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.52,0:06:51.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您在召集全城的年轻女孩…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:55.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些女孩到哪去了呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.34,0:06:59.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这件事你不必知道！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:04.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请…请原谅我…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.81,0:07:05.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我太无礼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.53,0:07:13.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕…我好想回甲斐国…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.92,0:07:19.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,绝对没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.33,0:07:22.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一股浓烈的妖气
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.87,0:07:25.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里面一定有人持有四魂之玉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:27.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我要一口气跳上去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.93,0:07:28.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上来吧 戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.86,0:07:33.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂！你怎么也上来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.43,0:07:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也要到这城里办事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.40,0:07:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那你就自己爬上去！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.03,0:07:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,顺便带他上去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.71,0:07:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.09,0:07:41.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的 拿你们没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.16,0:07:43.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,抓紧一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.36,0:08:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这座城也太没有戒备了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.70,0:08:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.94,0:08:08.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉少爷 您要小心一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:10.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些人都是被妖术催眠了的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.74,0:08:11.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恐怕…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.05,0:08:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城里的所有人都…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.58,0:08:20.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主！露姬公主大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.86,0:08:23.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露姬公主大人 您在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.22,0:08:26.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信长来救您了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.89,0:08:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主 露姬公主大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.17,0:08:32.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样好吗？他叫得这么大声
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.39,0:08:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,无所谓 反正大家都被妖术催眠了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.07,0:08:38.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们闹得这么大声 说不定妖怪自己会找上门来
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.07,0:08:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露姬公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.21,0:08:45.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您振作一点
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.42,0:08:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主 您怎么变成这个样子了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.15,0:08:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 信长君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.36,0:08:58.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你找的公主是不是这一位啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.40,0:09:04.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好美丽的公主啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.30,0:09:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我得把她唤醒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.00,0:09:08.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我开动啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.77,0:09:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.81,0:09:18.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信长…你怎么会在这里呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.38,0:09:21.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露姬公主大人 您还认得我吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.15,0:09:24.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我怎么可能会忘记你呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.15,0:09:25.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对我而言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.42,0:09:28.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是一个温柔又善良的青梅竹马
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我真是太幸福了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.93,0:09:33.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我只是一个家臣的小儿子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.96,0:09:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还以为您早就把我忘记了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:38.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你以前常掉进水池
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.33,0:09:40.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或是踩到马粪滑倒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:43.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,常常在逗我笑
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.04,0:09:48.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.78,0:09:51.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看信长君是不是喜欢这位公主啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.24,0:09:53.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切！真是无聊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.31,0:09:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真想回到那个时候…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.32,0:09:59.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:02.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主公的样子开始变得不太对劲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.66,0:10:05.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我嫁到这里不久后的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:09.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他突然昏倒在院子的池塘边
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,随后便发起高烧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.33,0:10:14.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那以后就好像变了个人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.67,0:10:17.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,简直像另一种生物一样
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:20.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信长 我该怎么办才好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.44,0:10:23.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这还用说吗？当然是跟我回甲斐国！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.94,0:10:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,此地城主发狂的传闻
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.08,0:10:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也已经传到我国主公那里了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.51,0:10:30.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以主公才会命令我来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,将公主带回去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.22,0:10:34.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是我父亲的命令？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:37.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就算没有命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.99,0:10:39.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.19,0:10:40.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信长…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.73,0:10:44.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露姬公主大人 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.26,0:10:47.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信长 你头上…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日吉丸…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.24,0:10:55.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看来它终于出场了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.51,0:10:57.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧 戈薇
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.88,0:11:05.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可疑的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.65,0:11:09.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总算出现了啊 你这个怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:12.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我露出你的真面目！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.53,0:11:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛤…蛤蟆？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.67,0:11:20.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主公…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.04,0:11:24.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公…公主 您振作一点啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.07,0:11:30.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看到四魂之玉了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.64,0:11:33.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算有四魂之玉 看起来还是很弱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.28,0:11:35.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉少爷 您千万不能大意
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.38,0:11:38.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙是至少300岁的妖怪 九十九蟾蜍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.95,0:11:40.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能用一般的方法来对付他
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.16,0:11:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切！我一拳就能把你打烂！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:49.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 这是瘴气
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.96,0:11:51.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 千万不要吸进去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.70,0:11:53.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你什么时候跑过来的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.31,0:12:01.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.81,0:12:04.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,退下！怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.81,0:12:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋 耍什么威风
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:09.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过是区区的人类
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.85,0:12:14.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信长君
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.22,0:12:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.56,0:12:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公…公主
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.56,0:12:22.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要乱动 你受了很重的伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.17,0:12:25.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是拼上我这一条性命…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.47,0:12:27.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也一定要救出公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.47,0:12:28.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信长君…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.70,0:12:32.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的很喜欢公主呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.24,0:12:34.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…你怎么知道的？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.68,0:12:36.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算隐瞒的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那只臭蛤蟆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.61,0:12:41.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我非宰了它不可
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.35,0:12:44.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我先过去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.99,0:12:47.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.62,0:12:48.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.00,0:12:58.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露姬公主 我喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.23,0:13:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把你吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.54,0:13:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你了！臭蛤蟆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经太迟了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.74,0:13:13.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.18,0:13:14.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露姬公主大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.02,0:13:20.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像传闻中所说的 这些人就像是蟾蜍的卵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.52,0:13:25.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,九十九蟾蜍就是在\N等这些女孩的灵魂成熟之后再吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.89,0:13:29.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这家伙利用四魂之玉的力量取得了城主的身份
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.16,0:13:32.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后占据了整个领地吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.50,0:13:33.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.67,0:13:36.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想吃掉露姬公主大人吗！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:40.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你这可恶的家伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.21,0:13:42.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是瘴气 快点让开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.18,0:13:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛤蟆城主 看招！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.91,0:13:45.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.03,0:13:49.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他能够自由使用铁碎牙了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.58,0:13:52.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为这也算是帮助人类
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:54.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要用铁碎牙 把你肚子剖开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.55,0:13:57.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后把四魂之玉碎片取出来
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:14:02.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我快死了 灵魂…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.33,0:14:05.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,灵魂！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.54,0:14:25.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复活了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.99,0:14:27.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,伤口痊愈了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.45,0:14:28.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.09,0:14:30.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你尽量砍啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.76,0:14:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你砍我多少刀
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.23,0:14:35.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我就吃多少个灵魂！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.50,0:14:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主 露姬公主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.47,0:14:46.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:47.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信长…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.74,0:14:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信长！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.54,0:14:51.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露…露姬公主大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.65,0:14:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的人生再也没有遗憾了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.75,0:14:58.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想对公主做什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.49,0:15:02.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你没有资格这么说
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.16,0:15:12.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露姬…公主
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.18,0:15:17.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.82,0:15:22.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这…这些…都是我干的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.66,0:15:25.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在装什么傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.11,0:15:27.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个声音…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.28,0:15:29.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是以前那个温柔的城主的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:33.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗 真正的城主还活在蛤蟆体内
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.52,0:15:34.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肯定的！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:38.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这实在…实在是太可怕了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.03,0:15:41.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我竟然… 做出这么可怕的事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.66,0:15:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我刚开始 被这只怪物附身的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.30,0:15:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还保有一颗人类的心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:51.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是这段时间…连人类的心也…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.04,0:15:53.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杀了我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.54,0:15:57.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再这么下去 我会连露姬都吃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.54,0:15:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主公
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.58,0:16:00.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求你们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.58,0:16:02.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我跟这只蛤蟆精一起砍死吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.48,0:16:05.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你倒是挺懂道理的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.58,0:16:07.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真不愧是城主
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.72,0:16:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我不客气了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.66,0:16:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等等 犬夜叉 主公会怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:15.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是嘛 他还保有一颗人类的心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.86,0:16:17.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吵死了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.50,0:16:19.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是城主自己叫我杀他的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.70,0:16:21.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没必要有这么无聊的同情心
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.77,0:16:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.74,0:16:25.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把刀收起来 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.54,0:16:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这怪物的体内还残留着城主的心！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.21,0:16:30.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混蛋…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.71,0:16:33.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再不让开我连你一起砍死！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.38,0:16:34.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那可不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:35.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那快让开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.51,0:16:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那也不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.78,0:16:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能眼睁睁看着\N你杀掉灵魂还活着的主公殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.92,0:16:42.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 就算他不是主公
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.29,0:16:45.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不想看到任何人死去！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:47.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信长君…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:49.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道在这个战乱时代说这种天真话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.03,0:16:52.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定会被嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:54.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使如此我还是…我还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.45,0:17:07.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.51,0:17:09.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我再也不会出手了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.32,0:17:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下来你们自己解决好了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.99,0:17:17.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.26,0:17:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你帮我求情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:31.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信长君！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.04,0:17:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它变回原形了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.67,0:17:37.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信长 信长！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.71,0:17:38.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.25,0:17:41.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是我动手的话主公会死掉哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.55,0:17:44.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露姬…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.55,0:17:48.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇小姐 你不要管我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.12,0:17:49.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快带公主逃走…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.89,0:17:52.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.96,0:17:54.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信长…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.27,0:18:00.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滚开！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.57,0:18:09.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,白痴 你清醒点没有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.61,0:18:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,千…千万不要杀他…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.34,0:18:14.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.31,0:18:15.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.56,0:18:26.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什么…有什么好办法吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.36,0:18:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽说是九十九蟾蜍 其实也只是只蛤蟆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.86,0:18:31.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它应该很怕烫的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.53,0:18:32.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,烫的东西？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.67,0:18:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以用开水泼它
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.60,0:18:35.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,开水？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.37,0:18:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么以来蟾蜍就会痛苦地从主公身体里逃出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.74,0:18:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你这么说 你叫我现在到那里去找开水啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:44.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.44,0:18:46.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.75,0:18:49.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,站住…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.75,0:18:51.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有没有什么烫的东西…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.38,0:18:52.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 火！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.85,0:18:54.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里有没有像是火把那样大的火
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:58.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,日吉丸…你什么时候…？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.86,0:19:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要把你们两个吃掉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.80,0:19:14.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是火！ 你真聪明 日吉丸
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.77,0:19:17.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太小了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.15,0:19:28.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我站住 臭蛤蟆！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.69,0:19:30.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.56,0:19:33.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戈薇 现在没有时间再说什么大道理了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.56,0:19:34.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要动手了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.89,0:19:36.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我哪有说什么大道理…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.63,0:19:38.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对了 定型喷雾
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.33,0:19:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以的 这个能把蛤蟆精赶出来
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.67,0:19:44.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有杀了它了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.97,0:19:46.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我坐下！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.41,0:19:46.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.18,0:19:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.32,0:19:57.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 四魂之玉碎片！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.82,0:19:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还用得着你说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.69,0:20:01.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要砍碎你！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.76,0:20:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,犬夜叉 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.10,0:20:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了 你做的真是太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.00,0:20:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主公总算得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.97,0:20:20.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没想到你真的忍耐到蟾蜍离开主公的身体了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.71,0:20:22.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有啦 我不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.94,0:20:24.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就当作是这样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.44,0:20:26.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.16,0:20:32.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露…露姬公主大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.35,0:20:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信长
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.22,0:20:35.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露姬公主
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.02,0:20:38.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你保护了主公
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.19,0:20:39.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,露姬公主…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.63,0:20:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主公 您终于恢复原来清爽的样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.56,0:20:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起 让你受苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.67,0:20:49.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这位城主挺温柔的呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.73,0:20:50.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,切～
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.14,0:20:53.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,蛤蟆精的妖术解开之后
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.57,0:20:55.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些女孩子们也都得救了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.87,0:20:57.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.65,0:21:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个…提起精神来 信长君…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.75,0:21:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是受不了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.05,0:21:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个家伙果然是个大傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.75,0:21:10.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自己都差点没命了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:12.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然还帮自己的情敌求情
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.66,0:21:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说的没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.26,0:21:21.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的确是个比织田信长还笨的大傻瓜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.10,0:21:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是呢 也正因为你有这股傻劲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.17,0:21:26.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才能救得了那么多人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.27,0:21:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是挺好的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 这下有精神了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.02,0:21:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.46,0:21:39.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦？要去哪里…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.09,0:21:41.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,信长 那边是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.36,0:21:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那边是断崖啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.56,0:21:48.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他还真是个迷糊虫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.76,0:22:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}一味地  只知道逞强的我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.03,0:22:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}但是  从那时起我不再茫然
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.87,0:22:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}一定有想要与你分享的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.62,0:22:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}也有许多想向你倾诉的话语
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.92,0:22:36.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}无论是笑容还是泪颜都想呈现给你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.82,0:22:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}等待着  将曾经放弃的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.90,0:22:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}机会重新抓住
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.07,0:22:51.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}我想着你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.94,0:22:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}只要如此  便觉得心变得坚强
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.16,0:23:06.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}这份渺茫的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.44,0:23:11.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}无论何时都在祈祷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.39,0:23:16.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\4c&HF4E7FC&\3c&HF25B5F&}希望能够传达给你…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.41,0:23:30.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从古井出来之后 到了战国时代
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.04,0:23:34.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说不定有一天能够遇上真正的 信长 秀吉 家康哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.05,0:23:37.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然历史成绩会因此提高不少
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.98,0:23:39.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,签名本也变得必不可缺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.08,0:23:42.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,照相机说不定也派得上用场
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.49,0:23:46.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过要是拍到妖怪 我可不想再看了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.49,0:23:48.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 发现一个好可爱的妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.96,0:23:50.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,次回 犬夜叉
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.26,0:23:53.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七宝登场！雷兽兄弟 飞天满天！！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.70,0:23:55.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,敬请期待
